description: Student newspaper of the University of New Hampshire
label: The New Hampshire
title: The_New_Hampshire
exrest: The New Hampshire is the student-run news of the University of New Hampshire (UNH) since 1911. TNH operates from its headquarters in the Memorial Union Building, covering student life and doings for the college town of Durham, as well as nearby cities like Dover and Newmarket.
